{"type":"message","id":"0312173d","parentId":"cc7e1fff","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:57:06.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，服务器上有Python3和Node环境。我来给姚总设计一个简单可行的方案：\n\n**最简方案：Python http.server + 内网穿透**\n\nPython自带一个简单的HTTP服务器，可以快速启动文件服务。但需要内网穿透才能从外网（飞书）访问。\n\n让我检查一下有没有现成的内网穿透工具。","thinkingSignature":"3df6b79ba02a94a917e6b3e711902304a68338eff68ed3dd5f752b301a88d5ea"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mssh6ax7p966_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which ngrok 2>/dev/null || which frp 2>/dev/null || echo \"no tunnel tool found\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2592,"output":119,"cacheRead":56166,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58877,"cost":{"input":0.0007775999999999999,"output":0.0001428,"cacheRead":0.0016849799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0026053799999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774400221720}}
