{"type":"message","id":"40f15805","parentId":"c72be6a5","timestamp":"2026-03-25T01:42:18.141Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"所有4位员工的完整版日报点评已发送完毕。每位员工收到的都是：做得好的+需改进+建议+总分，这四部分内容和确认版完全一致，一字不差。","thinkingSignature":"3d53425b931471bd3a1919804c4ea06950881159dce4c54864362b59d0666f73"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **4位员工完整版日报点评已重新发送！**\n\n这次发的内容是：做得好的 + 需改进 + 建议 + 总分，四部分和确认版完全一致，一字不差。\n\n请过目。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64298,"output":90,"cacheRead":56166,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120554,"cost":{"input":0.019289399999999998,"output":0.000108,"cacheRead":0.0016849799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021082379999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774402934157}}
