{"type":"message","id":"a390e257","parentId":"4d797cf1","timestamp":"2026-03-25T06:53:07.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，http server还在运行。现在让我重新启动穿透服务。我会尝试用localtunnel，这次指定一个更短的超时时间。实际上，问题在于localtunnel和serveo都不太稳定。让我想想其他方案。我可以尝试：1. 用npx localtunnel --subdomain 指定子域名\n2. 用npx serveo 指定子域名  \n3. 直接配置OpenClaw使用ngrok或其他服务其实最稳定的方案可能是配置OpenClaw使用Cloudflare Tunnel。让我看看OpenClaw是否已经支持Cloudflare Tunnel配置。或者，让我尝试npx localtunnel，并用一个稳定的后台进程来维持它。","thinkingSignature":"63a9b9a909f4dfcc95d96cb1267dbb44f97bf20aa0803644f5d9b7204baa5365"},{"type":"text","text":"让我用localtunnel重新创建一个稳定链接：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c968x3e4pmqj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp && rm -f localtunnel.log 2>/dev/null; nohup npx localtunnel --port 8899 > localtunnel.log 2>&1 &\necho \"Started, waiting...\"\nsleep 12\ncat localtunnel.log"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":13395,"output":220,"cacheRead":56230,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69845,"cost":{"input":0.0040184999999999995,"output":0.00026399999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0016868999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0059694}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774421578465}}
